984
00:35:26,180 --> 00:35:27,300
Since you're back,

985
00:35:28,860 --> 00:35:31,060
I'll take a few days off work.

986
00:35:31,820 --> 00:35:33,140
Let's visit and tidy up Mom's grave together.

987
00:35:34,580 --> 00:35:35,140
Sure.

988
00:35:36,020 --> 00:35:36,860
It's just right.

989
00:35:38,060 --> 00:35:39,380
I haven't seen Mom in a long time.

990
00:35:46,820 --> 00:35:48,380
You've grown up after staying abroad for a few years.

991
00:35:48,900 --> 00:35:49,820
Of course.

992
00:35:50,340 --> 00:35:51,780
I know that you care about me.

993
00:35:52,660 --> 00:35:53,820
Now that you're back,

994
00:35:54,700 --> 00:35:55,740
what's your plan?

995
00:35:56,930 --> 00:35:57,740
Didn't I tell you?

996
00:35:57,740 --> 00:35:58,660
I signed a contract with a company

997
00:35:59,500 --> 00:36:01,060
and they're planning to hold

998
00:36:01,060 --> 00:36:01,740
a solo recital for me.

999
00:36:02,700 --> 00:36:03,860
A solo recital?

1000
00:36:04,940 --> 00:36:06,170
I didn't provide for you for nothing.

1001
00:36:06,700 --> 00:36:08,820
You're starting off at a very high point.

1002
00:36:09,820 --> 00:36:12,380
Didn't you just win

1003
00:36:13,020 --> 00:36:14,100
the Best New Artist Award abroad?

1004
00:36:14,260 --> 00:36:15,660
Now you're having a solo concert right after coming back.

1005
00:36:16,020 --> 00:36:16,940
You've made it.

1006
00:36:18,060 --> 00:36:18,580
Here.

1007
00:36:39,350 --> 00:36:41,410
[Lin Luxiao transferred 5,000 yuan]

