Captain Meng.

1022
00:38:08,700 --> 00:38:10,460
This is great. Think about it.

1023
00:38:10,860 --> 00:38:11,860
Not only

1024
00:38:12,140 --> 00:38:14,140
can this show showcase a good image of firefighters,

1025
00:38:14,460 --> 00:38:16,540
but also help us

1026
00:38:16,540 --> 00:38:18,260
broaden our promotion of fire safety measures,

1027
00:38:18,660 --> 00:38:19,420
and even help the general public

1028
00:38:19,420 --> 00:38:20,860
understand fire safety knowledge.

1029
00:38:21,060 --> 00:38:23,060
It's killing three birds with one stone. Of course we'll do it.

1030
00:38:23,060 --> 00:38:24,580
You can count on us for this.

1031
00:38:24,980 --> 00:38:25,540
We will complete the task.

1032
